      "content": "\"let the journey end\"... that's a heavy way to put it. but you get what i mean, right? like if you've seen everything there is to see, staying on the road just feels like running in circles. it's almost more peaceful to just accept that the trip is done. it's like, instead of dreading the long journey back, shouldn't i just embrace the finality of it?",
